data.description: Welcome to 4 Coy Park Dr located on quiet street in a quaint rural town. Open the front door to a bright and open living room. The kitchen boasts custom cabinetry with plenty of storage.  The custom island with additional countertop space as well as behind-door storage. French doors in the dining area allow for a ton of natural light. Recent updates to this home include new roof in 2022, new gas stove, new refrigerator, new washer 2023, dishwasher 2021. Furnace, AC and whole house Dukane humidifier are 6 years old. Home has been freshly painted with new flooring in Living room and kitchen/dining room in September 2023.   French doors open to an expansive low maintenance raised deck.   At the bottom of the deck stairs, leading to the yard, is a cozy brick patio area complete with curved brick sitting wall. This home sits on an amazing half-acre property full of mature trees with a winding creek running along the back yard. Newer Hurd windows throughout. In addition, the washer and dryer are being housed in a bedroom closet for ease of use, and can be relocated to the basement.  The basement is partially finished with a room/4th bedroom (or office) and a second bathroom that will be great with a bit of TLC.  Basement has  a large area/rec room/multipurpose room.  The possibilities are endless! An additional unfinished room provides storage and the utility area is large enough for even more storage.   The home has an attached one car garage with a double wide driveway, allowing for parking for approximately four or more cars. The elementary school and high school are just around the corner. Pre-School is in Plano.  House is not far from shopping in Yorkville, Plano, Sandwich, and Oswego. Close access to major highways.  Seller providing a HWA 13 month Diamond home warranty for your peace of mind.  Sells As-is.   Motivated Sellers!
